    <p class="page-text mt-[20px]">
      The workflow is designed for speed and clarity: build prescriptions with
      reusable templates, structured medications, lab tests, and doctor notes;
      export high-quality PDFs for prescriptions, bills, and certificates; and
      share documents via WhatsApp. Billing tools let you generate itemized
      bills, track paid/pending status, and maintain an activity log for recent
      actions and history exports. A responsive, polished UI with light/dark
      modes keeps the experience smooth across devices.
    </p>
