    <p class="page-text mt-[30px]">
      Under the hood, it uses Next.js and React with Tailwind CSS for a fast,
      accessible interface, Lucide Icons and Sonner for UI polish and
      notifications, and NextAuth with Google OAuth for secure authentication.
      Data is managed via Local Storage and an optional custom database, while a
      custom PDF generator produces professional documents. Built-in WhatsApp
      integration and deployment-friendly architecture make it easy to adopt in
      real-world clinics.
    </p>
