    <p class="page-text mt-[20px]">
      This project is a modern, responsive web portal for the Indian Institute
      of Information Technology, Bhopal. It presents a clean, accessible
      interface that consolidates institute-wide information for students,
      faculty, researchers, and visitors. The site highlights key areas such as
      departments, research, academics, notices, events, placements, and campus
      life, providing a cohesive experience with fast navigation and clear
      content hierarchy.
    </p>
