    <p class="page-text mt-[20px]">
      The application offers dynamic navigation with multi-level dropdowns,
      auto-scrolling updates that pause on hover, skeleton placeholders for
      smooth loading, “NEW” indicators for fresh content, and image modals for
      enhanced viewing. It integrates social media feeds and features rich
      sections like department overviews, program details and syllabi, research
      highlights, notice and tender boards, media galleries, and student project
      showcases—making it both informative and engaging.
    </p>
